wdi2-SH.PRG.ANEM.def: Prevalence of anemia, pregnant women, is the percentage of pregnant women whose hemoglobin level is less than 110 grams per liter at sea level.
wdi2-SH.PRG.ANEM.name: Prevalence of anemia among pregnant women
wdi2-SH.PRG.ANEM.source: World Health Organization, Global Health Observatory Data Repository/World Health Statistics.
